         <div xml:lang="la">
            <p>Omnibus præsens scriptum cernentibus, Johannes dei gratia episcopus Otthoniensis
               salutem in domino <app>
                  <lem>perhennalem</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>sempiternam</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>eternalem</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app>. </p>
            <p>Tenore præsentium notum sit præsentibus et futuris, quod nos ex deliberato animo
               maturoque consilio, ob remedium et salutem anime nostræ <app>
                  <lem>animarumque</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>nostrarumque</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> parentum et progenitorum nostrorum, nec non omnium fratrum et sororum, vivorum
               et mortuorum, convivii sancti Canuti in <app>
                  <lem>Svineborigh</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Svineborg</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app>, omne jus et universam justitiam quæ nobis juste competit in bonis, nobis per
               famosum virum dominum <app>
                  <lem>Bernichinum</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Vernichinum</q> Aa, Aa2, Aa3, Ad</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Wernichinum</q> Aa1, Aa1a</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Vernickinum</q> Ab1</rdg>
               </app>
               <app>
                  <lem>Skynkel</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Skynkil</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ad</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Sckinkil</q> Ab1</rdg>
               </app>, militem, pro centum quinquaginta march. <app>
                  <lem>lubsk</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>lubic.</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> in <app>
                  <lem>Hundzstrop</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Hunstrup</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Huustrup</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app> et <app>
                  <lem>Möndorp</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Möndrop</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Möndrup</q> Ab1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Mondr{ue}p</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app> provinciæ <app>
                  <lem>Salinge-Herrit</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Sallingherret</q> Aa, Aa1a</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Sallingherred</q> Aa1, Aa3</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Sallingherredt</q> Ab1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Salingherredt</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app> sitis, per apertas literas suas inpigneratis, ad <app>
                  <lem>
                     <app>
                        <lem>unam</lem>
                        <rdg>således Aa, Aa2, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
                        <rdg>
                           <q>suam</q> Ac1</rdg>
                     </app> vicariam</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>unum vicarium</q> Aa1, Aa1a, Aa3</rdg>
               </app> in ecclesia Beatæ Virginis in Suineborgh, ad laudem et honorem omnipotentis <app>
                  <lem>dei</lem>
                  <rdg>herefter tilføjet <q>et</q>, Ab1</rdg>
               </app>, in reverentiam gloriosi corporis et sanguinis domini nostri Jesu Christi,
               beatissimæ virginis genitricis suæ, et beati Canuti regis et martyris, <app>
                  <lem>omniumque</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>-que</q> udeladt i Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2 og Aa3</rdg>
               </app> sanctorum, de novo per nos fundandam et dotandam, cum omnibus et singulis
               conditionibus et articulis contentis in <app>
                  <lem>dictis</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>istis</q> Ab1</rdg>
               </app> literis apertis, nobis per prædictum dominum Bernichinum super <app>
                  <lem>hujusmodi</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>ejusmodi</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3</rdg>
               </app> bonorum <app>
                  <lem>inpignerationem</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>impignerationem</q> Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>ingignerationem</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2</rdg>
               </app> confectis, ad perpetuam possessionem damus, assignamus et <app>
                  <lem>scotamus</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>dotamus</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> veraciter per <app>
                  <lem>præsentes</lem>
                  <rdg>Herefter begynder der i Ab1, modsat de øvrige tekstvidner, ikke en ny
                     periode</rdg>
               </app>. </p>
            <p>Tali cum modo, quod quandocunque antedicta bona, pro præfata pecuniæ summa, secundum
               continentiam literarum, super hoc ut præfertur, confectarum, legaliter redempta
               fuerint, ex <app>
                  <lem>tunc</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>tempore</q> øvrige</rdg>
               </app> ipsa pecunia, secundum ordinationem et consilium plebani ecclesiæ beatæ
               virginis supradictæ senatoris convivii regis Canuti, de quo supra, et potiorum
               fratrum ejus, pro aliis redditibus ad sustentationem prænominatæ vicariæ valentibus,
               dispensetur, et utiliter ordinetur. </p>
            <p>Hoc insuper non neglecto, quod <app>
                  <lem>quotidiana</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>cottidiana</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> missa coram præfato altari, in <app>
                  <lem>quinta</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>prima</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> feria <app>
                  <lem>scilicet</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>sit</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> de glorioso corpore Christi, et in secunda feria pro omnibus fidelibus
               defunctis, cantanda, in ceterisque diebus legenda perpetuis <app>
                  <lem>temporibus</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>partibus</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> debeat celebrari. </p>
            <p>Volumus etiam quod prædicti, plebanus, senator et potiores fratres dicti convivii,
               jus patronatus seu præsentationis <app>
                  <lem>libere</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>liberum</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> ad vicariam habeant supra dictam.</p>
            <p>Præterea, si vicarius præfati altaris remissus et negligens fuerit, <app>
                  <lem>eandemque missam non celebraverit vel celebrari fecerit</lem>
                  <rdg>udeladt i Aa1 og Aa1a</rdg>
               </app> ex <app>
                  <lem>tunc</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>tempore</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> antedicti, plebanus et senatur, cum consilio dictorum fratrum de alio vicario <app>
                  <lem>utiliori</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>utili</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app>, qui <app>
                  <lem>astrictus</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>assiduus</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> sit ad ipsam missam tenendam, ut <app>
                  <lem>præfertur</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>præfatum</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app>, libere providebunt.</p>
            <p>In quarum fundationis et dotationis evidentiam firmiorem, sigillum nostrum una cum
               sigillo <app>
                  <lem>dilecti capituli</lem>
                  <rdg>Diplomatarium Danicums rettelse</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>dicti capituli</q> Ac1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>dilecti capellani</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1, Ad</rdg>
               </app> nostri, nobiliumque virorum, videlicet domini Nicolai dicti <app>
                  <lem>Bild</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Biil</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3, Ab1</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>Bul</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app>, militis, et Jacobi Herlugson, fratruelis nostri, præsentibus duximus <app>
                  <lem>appendendum</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>apponendum</q> Ad</rdg>
               </app>.</p>
            <p>Datum et actum anno domini M.C.D. <app>
                  <lem>decimo septimo</lem>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>decimo septimo</q> Ac1 og Ad</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>decimo 7timo</q> Aa, Aa1, Aa1a, Aa2, Aa3</rdg>
                  <rdg>
                     <q>XVII</q> Ab1</rdg>
               </app>, in vigilia assumptionis beatæ Mariæ virginis.</p>
         </div>
